AEGON U.S. Holding Corp, aunit of AEGON N.V. of the Netherlands, and Life Investors Inc&lt;LINV.O> said they have purchased about 451,000 shares of LifeInvestors common stock for 51.61 dlrs per share cash.    The purchase is part of an agreement between the twocompanies made in November 1981, saying that on or before eachApril 30 between 1983 and 1987 the companies would offer to buyone-sixth of the number of Life Investors' common stockoutstanding as of Dec. 31, 1982, not already owned by AEGON.    On Dec. 31 1988 they would offer to buy any and allremaining shares. Reuter&#3;